6quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20product%2C%20which%20is%20made%20by%20Texas-based%20company%20Paqui%2C%20consists%20of%20a%20single%20tortilla%20chip%20spiced%20with%20Naga%20viper%20and%20Carolina%20Reaper%20peppers%2C%20known%20as%20some%20of%20the%20hottest%20peppers%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20packaged%20in%20a%20coffin-shaped%20box%20decorated%20with%20a%20skull.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20were%20invited%20to%20see%20if%20they%20could%20handle%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20chip%20and%20post%20the%20results%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20Massachusetts%20family%20said%20that%20their%20fourteen-year-old%20son%2C%20Harris%20Wolobah%2C%20died%20hours%20after%20taking%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20Chip%20Challenge%26quot%3B%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fboston%2Fnews%2Fone-chip-challenge-death-paqui-harris-wolobah-worcester-massachusetts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%20affiliate%20WBZ-TV%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20body%20is%20at%20the%20medical%20examiner's%20office%2C%20and%20the%20official%20cause%20of%20death%20is%20still%20being%20determined%2C%20according%20to%20WBZ-TV.%20But%20his%20family%20is%20blaming%20the%20company%20for%20his%20death%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpaqui.com%2Fonechipchallenge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20statement%20posted%20to%20its%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Paqui%20said%20it%20was%20removing%20the%20chip%20from%20stores%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20chip%20still%20adheres%20to%20food-safety%20standards%20and%20pointed%20to%20its%20labeling%2C%20which%20it%20said%20indicated%20it%20was%20for%20adults%20only%2C%20with%20warnings%20advising%20against%20those%20with%20allergies%2C%20health%20condit