Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20for%20the%20UN%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20debate%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dujarric%2C%20who%20was%20speaking%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Delhi%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20the%20formalities%20are%20done%2C%20the%20UN%20will%20change%20the%20name%20too.%20It's%20a%20bureaucratic%20issue%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20what%20the%20UN%20needs%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20not%20be%20the%20first%20country%20if%2C%20at%20all%2C%20the%20name%20change%20happens.%20There's%20a%20long%20list%20of%20countries%20that%20have%20changed%20their%20names%20due%20to%20political%2C%20social%2C%20or%20other%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20official%20also%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Turkey%20changing%20its%20name%20to%20Turkiye%20last%20year%20and%20said%C2%A0%26quot%3Bhistory%20has%20shown%20that%20it%20has%20happened%20a%20number%20of%20times%20for%20several%20countries%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20planning%20to%20drop%20India%20and%20stay%20with%20just%20Bharat%20as%20the%20country's%20name.%20Several%20ministers%20and%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20said%20there%20need%20not%20be%20any%20controversy%20as%20'Bharat'%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bin%20use%20from%20time%20immemorial%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20recently%20spoke%20on%20the%20issue%20during%20his%20interaction%20with%20the%20Union%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20in%20which%20he%20laid%20down%20the%20dos%20and%20don'ts%20to%20be%20observed%20by%20them%20during%20the%20upcoming%20G20%20summit.%20He%20told%20his%20ministerial%20colleagues%20to%20avoid%20the%20political%20row%20around%20the%20Bharat%20issue%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20has%20been%20the%20country's%20ancient%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20Summit%20is%20being%20held%20in%20Delhi%20on%20September%209%20and%2010%20under%20India's%20presidency%20and%20several%20heads%20of%20state%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20are%20attending%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20presidency%20comes%20at%20a%20very%20critical%20time.%20India%20is%20a%20leading%20voice%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%20India%20is%20also%20a%20bridge%20builder%20politically%2C%20and%20geographically%20and%20the%20theme%20for%20this%20G20%20'One%20Earth%2C%20One%20Planet'%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20need%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dujarric%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694177580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fm47jr86_united-nations-geneva_625x300_05_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-change-indias-name-to-bharat-in-un-records-if-new-delhi-completes-formalities-un-spokesperson-to-ndtv-4371742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Will%20change%20India's%20name%20to%20Bharat%20in%20UN%20records%20if%20New%20Delhi%20completes%20formalities%3A%20UN%20spokesperson%20to%20NDTV%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-change-indias-name-to-bharat-in-un-records-if-new-delhi-completes-formalities-un-spokesperson-to-ndtv-4371742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-change-indias-name-to-bharat-in-un-records-if-new-delhi-completes-formalities-un-spokesperson-to-ndtv-4371742%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-change-indias-name-to-bharat-in-un-records-if-new-delhi-completes-formalities-un-spokesperson-to-ndtv-4371742%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden%2C%20In%20India%20For%20G20%2C%20To%20Stay%20At%20This%20Delhi%20Hotel.%20Details%20Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20on%20his%20way%20to%20India%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20Biden%2C%20wh