0right%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20hosting%20the%20summit.%20%26quot%3BThe%20G20%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20success%20for%20India...%20(I)%20feel%20we%20will%20have%20a%20very%20good%20couple%20of%20days%20of%20deliberations%20and%20decisions...%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20assumes%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20-%20which%20rotates%20between%20member%20nations%20-%20for%202023%20and%20a%20decked-up%20national%20capital%20will%20play%20host%20to%20the%2019%20other%20members%20over%20the%20next%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694176800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-08%2Furn5beog_rishi-sunak-reuters-650_625x300_09_August_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-in-india-for-g20-says-on-khalistani-threats-wont-tolerate-extremism-in-the-uk-news-agency-ani-4371839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK%20is%20%26quot%3Bworking%20closely%20with%20India%20to%20tackle%20Khalistani%20extremism%26quot%3B%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20said%20Friday%20evening%2C%20shortly%20after%20landing%20in%20Delhi%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20the%20annual%20meet%20of%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20influential%20power%20blocs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-in-india-for-g20-says-on-khalistani-threats-wont-tolerate-extremism-in-the-uk-news-agency-ani-4371839%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-in-india-for-g20-says-on-khalistani-threats-wont-tolerate-extremism-in-the-uk-news-agency-ani-4371839%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frishi-sunak-in-india-for-g20-says-on-khalistani-threats-wont-tolerate-extremism-in-the-uk-news-agency-ani-4371839%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Forces%20Studying%20Options%20For%20Any%20China-Taiwan%20War%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20studying%20possible%20responses%20to%20a%20potential%20Chinese%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan%20following%20discreet%20inquiries%20from%20the%20US%20on%20how%20the%20country%20could%20contribute%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20war%2C%20according%20to%20senior%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20weeks%20ago%2C%20Defense%20Chief%20General%20Anil%20Chauhan%20-%20the%20top%20military%20commander%20-%20commissioned%20a%20study%20to%20examine%20the%20wider%20impact%20of%20any%20war%20over%20the%20island%20that%20also%20involves%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20and%20what%20action%20India%20could%20take%20in%20response%2C%20according%20to%20two%20senior%20Indian%20officials%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20since%20discussions%20are%20private.%20The%20order%20came%20after%20the%20US%20raised%20the%20issue%20in%20several%20different%20forums%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20will%20assess%20various%20war%20scenarios%20and%20provide%20options%20for%20India%20in%20case%20a%20conflict%20breaks%20out%2C%20they%20said.%20Some%20military%20commanders%20believe%20that%20strong%20statements%20may%20suffice%20as%20a%20response%20in%20case%20the%20war%20is%20short%2C%20but%20ultimately%20that%20will%20not%20be%20enough%20if%20the%20conflict%20drags%20on%20like%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20preparation%20for%20a%20potential%20war%20over%20Taiwan%20shows%20how%20its%20policy%20of%20%26quot%3Bmulti-alignment%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20tested%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20drastic%20deterioration%20of%20US-China%20ties.%20Under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20India%20has%20forged%20its%20own%20path%20on%20international%20relations%2C%20effectively%20hedging%20its%20bets%20by%20developing%20close%20ties%20to%20the%20US%20while%20refusing%20to%20join%20international%20sanctions%20on%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20tensions%20with%20China%20have%20also%20flared%20along%20their%20disputed%20Himalayan%20border%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20deterioration%20in%20relations%20that%20may%20have%20prompted%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20to%20skip%20the%20Group%20of%2020%20summit%20this%20weekend%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20India%20has%20strengthened%20defense%20ties%20with%20the%20US%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20joining%20the%20Quadrilateral%20Security%20Dialogue%20along%20with%20Japan%20and%20Australia%20-%20a%20band%20of%20democracies%20intent%20on%20countering%20China's%20growing%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20option%20the%20Indian%20military%20will%20study%20involves%20serving%20as%20a%20logistics%20hub%20to%20provide%20repair%20and%20maintenance%20facilities%20for%20allied%20warships%20and%20aircraft%2C%20as%20well%20as%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20medical%20equipment%20for%20armies%20resisting%20China%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%20A%20more%20extreme%20scenario%2C%20they%20added%2C%20would%20assess%20the%20potential%20for%20India%20to%20get%20directly%20involved%20along%20their%20northern%20border%2C%20opening%20a%20new%20theater%20of%20war%20for%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20no%20deadline%20has%20been%20set%20to%20complete%20the%20study%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20is%20under%20orders%20to%20finish%20it%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20one%20of%20the%20officials%20said.%20The%20options%20prepared%20will%20be%20available%20for%20PM%20Modi%20and%20other%20political%20leaders%20to%20make%20a%20final%20call%20on%20any%20action%20should%20the%20need%20arise%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20and%20Foreign%20ministries%20didn't%20respond%20to%20emailed%20questions.%20The%20US%20State%20Department%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20hyping%20up%20the%20Taiwan%20question%2C%20creating%20tensions%20and%20provoking%20confrontation%2C%20the%20US%20attempts%20to%20turn%20the%20Taiwan%20question%20into%20an%20international%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20Mao%20Ning%2C%20a%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokeswoman%2C%20told%20reporters%20in%20Beijing%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20highly%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20have%20mobilized%20thousands%20of%20troops%2C%20artillery%20guns%2C%20tanks%20and%20missiles%20closer%20to%20the%20unmarked%20border%20running%20some%203%2C500%20km%2C%20roughly%20the%20length%20of%20the%20US-Mexico%20boundary.%20Diplomatic%20talks%20have%20yielded%20little%2C%20with%20China%20last%20month%20releasing%20a%20new%20map%20claiming%20India-controlled%20territory%20that%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20publicly%20resisted%20efforts%20to%20make%20the%20Quad%20appear%20like%20a%20military%20alliance%2C%20and%20remains%20reliant%20on%20Russia%20-%20China's%20most%20important%20diplomatic%20partner%20-%20for%20weapons%20that%20would%20be%20used%20in%20any%20regional%20war.%20Even%20so%2C%20it%20has%20quietly%20sought%20better%20relations%20with%20Taiwan%3A%20Three%20former%20Indian%20military%20chiefs%20who%20stepped%20down%20in%20the%20past%20year%20all%20visited%20Taiwan%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%2C%20India%20and%20the%20US%20signed%20a%20Logistics-Exchange%20Memorandum%20of%20Agreement%2C%20a%20foundational%20pact%20to%20allow%20refueling%20and%20replenishing%20of%20warships%20and%20aircraft%2C%20as%20well%20as%20access%20to%20bases%20when%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20India%20is%20examining%20military%20options%2C%20it%20remains%20unlikely%20that%20the%20nation%20would%20get%20involved%20directly%20in%20a%20war%20over%20Taiwan%2C%20according%20to%20Lisa%20Curtis%2C%20senior%20fellow%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Security%20Program%20at%20the%20Washington-based%20Centre%20for%20a%20New%20American%20Security%2C%20who%20earlier%20worked%20with%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20CIA%20and%20the%20State%20Department.%20It's%20possible%20India%20may%20provide%20access%20to%20places%20like%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20near%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20were%20to%20be%20some%20kind%20of%20conflict%20or%20crises%20in%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%2C%20I%20think%20India's%20position%20would%20be%20to%20stand%20back%20and%20not%20get%20militarily%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20they%20may%20support%20Taiwan%20with%20statements%20and%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20I%20think%20they%20would%20be%20very%20weary%20about%20providing%20any%20kind%20of%20military%20assistance%20to%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694176800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F7dkfj648_china-taiwan-missiles_625x300_22_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-forces-studying-options-for-any-china-taiwan-war-report-4371882%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20studying%20possible%20responses%20to%20a%20potential%20Chinese%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan%20following%20discreet%20inquiries%20from%20the%20US%20on%20how%20the%20country%20could%20contribute%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20war%2C%20according%20to%20senior%20government%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-forces-studying-options-for-any-china-taiwan-war-report-4371882%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-forces-studying-options-for-any-china-taiwan-war-report-4371882%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F