eploying%20Hindutva%20as%20well%20as%20caste%20calculations%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20lost%20the%20Ghosi%20assembly%20by-poll%20election%20in%20the%20state%20as%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20takes%20an%20unassailable%20lead.%20This%20is%20not%20only%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20SP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20particular%2C%20but%20a%20source%20of%20major%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20straight%20contest%20between%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20the%20NDA.%20The%20Congress%20did%20not%20field%20a%20nominee%20but%20supported%20the%20SP%20candidate.%20The%20Mayawati-led%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20did%20not%20contest%20the%20by-poll%2C%20maintaining%20its%20position%20of%20officially%20staying%20away%20from%20both%20NDA%20and%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGhosi%20did%20not%20make%20victorious%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20SP%20but%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20and%20this%20is%20also%20going%20to%20be%20the%20result%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20in%20a%20congratulatory%20note%20for%20voters%20of%20Ghosi.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20victory%20of%20positive%20politics%20and%20the%20defeat%20of%20communal%2C%20negative%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20said%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%20result%20reflected%20the%20success%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20new%20formula%20against%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ETeam%20INDIA%20hai%2C%20aur%20PDA%20(Pichda%20Dalit%20Alpsankhyak)%20rajneeti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%E2%80%99s%20veteran%20leader%20Sudhakar%20Singh%2C%20a%20two-time%20former%20MLA%2C%20looks%20set%20to%20defeat%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Ghosi.%20According%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20after%2025%20out%20of%2034%20rounds%2C%20Singh%20had%20secured%20over%2097%2C500%20votes%2C%20leading%20over%20Chauhan%20by%20a%20big%20margin%20of%20close%20to%2034%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20by-poll%20was%20held%20after%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20was%20the%20sitting%20SP%20MLA%2C%20resigned%20from%20his%20seat%20and%20party%20in%20July%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20BJP.%20With%20the%20return%20of%20OBC%20leaders%20Chauhan%20and%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20to%20its%20fold%20after%20a%20short%20stint%20with%20the%20SP%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20received%20a%20huge%20boost%20as%20it%20prepared%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%20However%2C%20the%20defeat%20in%20Ghosi%2C%20where%20not%20just%20Rajbhar%20but%20over%20a%20dozen%20ministers%20in%20the%20Adityanath%20cabinet%20including%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%20extensively%20campaigned%20for%20Chauhan%2C%20has%20put%20the%20BJP%20in%20an%20awkward%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20also%20played%20the%20Hindutva%20card%20openly%20while%20campaigning%20for%20the%20by-poll%20in%20Ghosi%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Mau%20district%20of%20Purvanchal%2C%20abutting%20Azamgarh.%20Addressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Ghosi%20on%20September%202%2C%20Adityanath%20reminded%20voters%20of%20the%20firing%20on%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekarsevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20Ayodhya%20ordered%20by%20the%20then%20Mulayam%20Singh%20government%20in%201990.%20Adityanath%20also%20linked%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%20to%20the%202005%20Mau%20communal%20violence.%20SP%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%20is%20important%20would%20be%20understood%20by%20those%20who%20closely%20felt%20the%202005%20riots%20in%20Mau.%20Under%20the%20then%20SP%20government%2C%20rioters%20and%20mafia%2C%20brandishing%20weapons%20openly%2C%20were%20killing%20Yadavs%20in%20some%20places%20and%20Dalits%20in%20others.%20The%20Congress%20government%20ruling%20at%20the%20Centre%20then%20did%20not%20say%20anything%20and%20the%20SP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20could%20not%20do%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adityanath.%20The%20chief%20minister%20also%20reminded%20voters%20how%20he%20reached%20Mau%20from%20Gorakhpur%20to%20intervene.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20MP%20of%20Gorakhpur%20then.%20And%20to%20fight%20these%20rioters%2C%20I%20came%20down%20from%20Gorakhpur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20generating%20loud%20applause%20from%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Adityanath%20did%20not%20name%20jailed%C2%A0%20former%20MLA%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%2C%20who%20has%20faced%20the%20biggest%20brunt%20of%20the%20Gangsters%20Act%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20he%20made%20an%20unmistakable%20reference%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mafia%20who%20were%20earlier%20brandishing%20weapons%2C%20today%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20a%20wheelchair%20begging%20for%20their%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Ansari%20had%20been%20accused%20of%20instigating%20the%20Mau%20riots.%20His%20son%20Abbas%20Ansari%20had%20stood%20second%20in%20Ghosi%20in%202017%2C%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Fagu%20Chauhan%20by%20a%20thin%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudhakar%20Singh%2C%20who%20won%20from%20Ghosi%20in%201996%20and%202012%2C%20had%20stood%20third%20in%202017.%20A%20Kshatriya%20by%20caste%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20defeat%20Chauhan%20in%20this%20by-poll%20despite%20heavy%20mobilisation%20of%20caste%20leaders%20in%20particular%20OBCs%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChauhan%20served%20as%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20in%20the%20Adityanath%20government%20from%202017%20to%202022%20before%20resigning%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20and%20joining%20the%20SP.%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20had%20served%20as%20minister%20for%20forest%2C%20environment%20and%20zoological%20gardens%2C%20in%20his%20resignation%20letter%20had%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20tampering%20with%20reservations%20for%20OBCs%20and%20Dalits%20and%20neglecting%20their%20interests%20despite%20coming%20to%20power%20through%20their%20support.%20Chauhan%20belongs%20to%20the%20Noniya%20Chauhan%20backward%20caste.%20Traditionally%20engaged%20in%20salt%20trading%2C%20the%20community%20is%20also%20known%20by%20other%20names%20such%20as%20Loniya-Chauhan%20and%20Gole-Thakur%2C%20and%20consider%20Prithviraj%20Chauhan%20among%20their%20icons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20scattered%20in%20parts%20of%20east%20UP%20but%20are%20an%20important%20vote%20bloc%20in%20rural%20areas%20adjoining%20Varanasi%2C%20Azamgarh%2C%20Chandauli%20and%20Mau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChauhan%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20twice%20as%20an%20SP%20candidate%2C%20in%201996%20and%202000.%20When%20Mayawati%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20in%202007%2C%20he%20shifted%20loyalties%20and%20in%202009%20won%20his%20first%20and%20only%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Ghosi%20on%20a%20BSP%20symbol.%20He%20was%20also%20appointed%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20BSP%20parliamentary%20party%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20seat%20to%20the%20BJP.%20And%20a%20year%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%2C%20Chauhan%20joined%20the%20saffron%20party%20and%20contested%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20Madhuban%20seat%20in%20the%202017%20assembly%20election.%20He%20won%20and%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20cabinet%20berth.%20In%202022%2C%20after%20rebelling%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20won%20from%20Ghosi%20on%20an%20SP%20ticket.%20However%2C%20he%20soon%20started%20distancing%20himself%20from%20the%20Opposition%20party%20and%20in%20July%20formally%20resigned%20as%20an%20MLA%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defeat%20in%20Ghosi%20reflects%20poorly%20on%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20who%20had%20just%20recently%20returned%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20actively%20campaigned%20in%20the%20constituency%2C%20which%20has%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20voters%20of%20the%20Rajbhar%20community%2C%20an%20OBC%20caste.%20By%20ensuring%20a%20BJP%20win%2C%20he%20could%20have%20demonstrated%20his%20indispensability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20this%20election%20also%20marked%20the%20return%20to%20active%20campaigning%20of%20Akhilesh%20%E2%80%98s%20uncle%20Shivpal%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20held%20several%20public%20meetings%20in%20the%20by-poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20of%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%20All-India%20Chauhan%20Federation%2C%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20July%20assumed%20significance%20as%20the%20party%20lacked%20a%20popular%20face%20from%20the%20community%20after%20six-time%20MLA%20Fagu%20Chauhan%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20governor%20of%20Bihar%20in%202019.%20Fagu%20Chauhan%20is%20the%20current%20governor%20of%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20rebellions%20by%20OBC%20leaders%20Swami%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20and%20others%20had%20caused%20heavy%20losses%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202022%2C%20the%20party%20was%20desperate%20to%20set%20its%20caste%20arithmetic%20right%20as%20it%20approached%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20sees%20Purvanchal%20as%20a%20problem%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20won%20273%20seats%20in%20the%20403-member%20assembly%20in%202022%2C%20it%20fared%20poorly%20in%20southern%20and%20central%20parts%20of%20east%20UP.%20A%20lot%20of%20the%20SP%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20125%20seats%20came%20from%20these%20backward%20regions.%20The%20BJP%20lost%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20Ghazipur%2C%20three%20out%20of%20four%20in%20Mau%2C%20five%20out%20of%20nine%20in%20Jaunpur%2C%20five%20out%20of%20seven%20in%20Ballia%2C%20all%20ten%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20four%20out%20of%20five%20in%20Basti%2C%20all%20five%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%20three%20out%20of%20six%20in%20Barabanki%2C%20all%20three%20in%20Kaushambi%20and%20five%20out%20of%20seven%20in%20Pratapgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%2C%20several%20BJP%20ministers%2C%20including%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20and%20Brijesh%20Pathak%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20allies%20Sanjay%20Nishad%2C%20Ashish%20Patel%20and%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20campaigned%20heavily%20for%20Chauhan.%20The%20party%20deployed%20minister%20Danish%20Azad%2C%20its%20Muslim%20face%2C%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Muslim%20voters%20in%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%20had%20even%20accused%20the%20local%20police%20and%20administration%20of%20working%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20trying%20to%20pressure%20people%20in%20Muslim%20areas%20against%20voting%20for%20it%20and%20harassing%20its%20workers.%20The%20party%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20chief%20election%20officer%20of%20UP%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20trying%20to%20influence%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20as%20Sudhakar%20Singh%20started%20building%20his%20lead%20over%20Chauhan%2C%20Nishad%20Party%20chief%20Sanjay%20Nishad%2C%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20under%20Adityanath%2C%20equated%20areas%20with%20a%20Muslim%20population%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20insinuated%20that%20the%20SP%20was%20ahead%20as%20only%20votes%20of%20Muslim%20areas%20had%20been%20counted%20till%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20boxes%20(EVMs)%20in%20Pakistan%20areas%20are%20counted%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20Pakistan%20is%20winning.%20But%20when%20the%20boxes%20in%20our%20areas%20come%20out%2C%20they%20(Pakistan)%20go%20out%20of%20the%20picture%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy-polls%20don%E2%80%99t%20generally%20reflect%20the%20larger%20mood%20of%20the%20people%20and%20it%20has%20been%20established%20in%20the%20last%20few%20elections%20that%20voters%20think%20differently%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20national%20elections.%20In%202018%20too%2C%20the%20SP-led%20alliance%20won%20three%20crucial%20Lok%20Sabha%20by-poll%20elections%20in%20UP%20%E2%80%93%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Kairana%20and%20Phulpur%20%E2%80%93%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%202019%20election%20result%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20different.%20However%2C%20under%20the%20ever-changing%20political%20situation%20and%20high%20charged%20campaign%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20dismiss%20the%20prospects%20of%20INDIA%2C%20the%20Ghosi%20win%20is%20a%20big%20boost%20to%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20and%20their%20workers%20as%20they%20prepare%20to%20take%20on%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Adityanath%20and%20co%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20campaigning%20in%20Ghosi%2C%20Akhilesh%20had%20said%20the%20by-poll%20was%20not%20an%20ordinary%20assembly%20election%20but%20a%20message%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20After%20the%20win%2C%20Akhilesh%20said%20UP%20would%20once%20again%20lead%20the%20charge%20for%20change%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694174665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08173312%2FF4tErMfbMAArKnN.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-using-all-might-bjp-loses-ghosi-assembly-seat-to-india-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20big%20lead%20in%20the%20Ghosi%20assembly%20seat%20is%20not%20only%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20of%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20and%20SP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20in%20particular%2C%20but%20a%20source%20of%20major%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-using-all-might-bjp-loses-ghosi-assembly-seat-to-india-in-uttar-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Queen%20Elizabeth%20remembered%20as%20gun%20salutes%20set%20to%20ring%20out%20for%20King%20Charles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publish