0reject%20them%20preemptively.%20But%20what%20if%20there%20was%20another%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20in%20both%20dating%20and%20other%20contexts%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20let%20my%20fears%20rule%20the%20show%2C%20I%20made%20a%20list%20of%20questions%20for%20Coambs%20and%20interviewed%20five%20other%20planners%20to%20compare%20my%20options.%20Unlike%20the%20child%20who%20felt%20abandoned%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20now%20had%20adult%20tools%20to%20advocate%20for%20myself.%20Coambs%20respected%20my%20questions%2C%20answered%20them%20thoughtfully%2C%20and%20emphasized%20that%20the%20choice%20ultimately%20lay%20with%20me.%20As%20I%20signed%20off%20Zoom%20that%20day%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20would%20only%20see%20progress%20with%20a%20financial%20planner%20if%20I%20showed%20up%20with%20courage%20and%20sincerity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWorking%20with%20a%20fee-only%20financial%20planner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20hiring%20Coambs.%20He%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffee-only-financial-advisor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efee-only%20fiduciary%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20meaning%20he%20doesn't%20profit%20from%20any%20investments%20he%20recommends%2C%20but%20instead%20charges%20a%20straightforward%20flat%20rate%20for%20our%20work%20together.%20(A%20tip%20for%20anyone%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhy-hire-fee-only-financial-advisor-2019-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehiring%20their%20first%20financial%20planner%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20A%20fee-only%20structure%20is%20meant%20to%20avoid%20conflicts%20of%20interest.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20hired%20him%20in%20July%202023%2C%20Coambs'%20rate%20was%20on%20a%20sliding%20scale%20based%20on%20a%20client's%20income%20and%20financial%20standing.%20It%20started%20at%20%245%2C000%20a%20year%20plus%201%25%20of%20the%20client's%20overall%20net%20worth.%20My%20payment%2C%20Coambs%20informed%20me%2C%2