3F%20That%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20lion%20has%20not%20roared%20is%20an%20embarrassment%20best%20forgotten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20lions%2C%20fountains%2C%20lasers%20and%20silver%20plates%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20what%20cultural%20representation%20of%20New%20India%20is%20being%20given%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20For%20a%20summit%20dubbed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98People%E2%80%99s%20Festival%E2%80%99%2C%20people%20have%20been%20kept%20far%20away.%20From%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Outer%20Ring%20Road%20till%20Red%20Fort%20in%20one%20corner%2C%20Rajghat%20at%20another%20and%20Humayun%E2%80%99s%20Tomb%20as%20well%2C%20central%20Delhi%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20fortress.%20The%20People%E2%80%99s%20Festival%20will%20be%20behind%20green%20cloth%20curtains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20issue%20larger%20than%20the%20mindless%20projection%20of%20power%20and%20pageantry%20by%20an%20unimaginative%20bureaucracy%20and%20a%20backward%20looking%20political%20class.%20How%20exactly%20do%20we%20wish%20to%20present%20India%20to%20the%20world%20and%20what%20is%20our%20understanding%20of%20Indian%20culture%20today%3F%20It%20is%20not%20a%20subject%20that%20many%20in%20power%20have%20been%20giving%20much%20attention%20to.%20The%20quality%20of%20political%20and%20bureaucratic%20leadership%20within%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%20in%20Delhi%20and%20its%20counterparts%20in%20states%20says%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20blame%20the%20government%20alone%3F%20India%E2%80%99s%20newly%20rich%2C%20the%20new%20billionaires%20from%20real%20estate%20and%20public%20infrastructure%20to%20finance%20and%20start-ups%2C%20are%20all%20redefining%20Indian%20culture.%20It%20is%20increasingly%20pop%2C%20filmi%20and%20pseudo-religious.%20Art%20counts%20if%20it%20is%20valued%20in%20crores.%20Artists%20count%20if%20they%20have%20secured%20invitations%20for%20themselves%20from%20galleries%20in%20Paris%20and%20New%20York.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20reign%20of%20the%20nouveau%20riche.%20From%20India%E2%80%99s%20newly%20built%20airports%20to%20the%20newly%20built%20Parliament%2C%20garishness%20is%20on%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'They%20Really%20Descend%20on%20Journalism%20They%20Don't%20Like'%3A%20Press%20Freedom%20in%20India%2C%20on%20the%20Eve%20of%20the%20G20%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fm20-india-press-freedom-g20-impunity-it-cell%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98They%20Really%20Descend%20on%20Journalism%20They%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Like%E2%80%99%3A%20Press%20Freedom%20in%20India%2C%20on%20the%20Eve%20of%20the%20G20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20icons%20of%20classical%20and%20modern%20Indian%20culture%20are%20rarely%20consulted%20or%20associated%20with%20planning%20how%20the%20state%20should%20project%20national%20culture%20globally.%20When%20in%20doubt%2C%20governments%20display%20either%20folk%20culture%20%E2%80%93%20from%20tribal%20dances%20to%20garbha%20and%20bhangra%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Bollywood%20music.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20great%20symbol%20of%20Indian%20culture%20is%20%E2%80%98Naatu%20Naatu%E2%80%99.%20It%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20Secretary-General%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20hosting%20MS%2C%20but%20the%20Oscars%20jury%20who%20will%20decide%20for%20the%20world%20how%20India%20will%20be%20represented.%20Even%20friendly%20heads%20of%20government%20humour%20Indian%20political%20leadership%20now%20with%20a%20Naatu%20Naatu%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20years%20ago%20I%20accompanied%20Marxist%20economist%20and%20then%20finance%20minister%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20late%20Ashok%20Mitra%2C%20for%20dinner%20at%20the%20home%20of%20a%20successful%20and%20powerful%20businessman%20and%20media%20baron.%20There%20were%20four%20of%20us%20around%20the%20table%20but%20the%20food%20on%20display%20could%20have%20fed%20a%20couple%20of%20dozen.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20Kolkata%20Marwari%20businessman%20would%20have%20had%20the%20gumption%20to%20place%20so%20much%20food%