2C%20there%20are%20two%20people%20missing%20in%20this%20team.%20First%2C%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%2C%20and%20second%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh.%20Because%20a%20left-arm%20seamer%2C%20if%20he%20can%20bring%20the%20new%20ball%20inside%2C%20it%20makes%20it%20useful%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Harbhajan%20Singh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20can%20get%20two%20wickets%20early%20in%20the%20game%2C%20I'm%20not%20saying%20that%20right-handers%20can't%20do%20that%2C%20but%20a%20left-hand%20seamer%20can%20get%20an%20actual%20angle%20to%20get%20the%20wicket.%20You%20can%20see%20how%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20or%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20give%20to%20give%20the%20example%20of%20Mitchell%20Starc%20for%20Australia%20at%20the%202025%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Australia%20won%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20Mitchell%20Starc%20had%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20the%20games%3B%20he%20sent%20Brendan%20McCullum%20out%20on%20the%20first%20ball.%20Incoming%20ball%2C%20with%20that%20speed%2C%20coming%20into%20a%20right-hander%20is%20always%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%20winner%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%2C%20being%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%2C%20a%20proven%20match-winner%2C%20someone%20who%20has%20taken%20more%20wickets%20than%20any%20other%20spinner.%20If%20he%20was%20playing%20for%20any%20other%20country%2C%20I%20would%20think%20he%20would%20always%20be%20in%20the%20playing%20XI.%20But%20even%20after%20proving%20so%20much%2C%20I%20feel%20he%20should%20have%20been%20in%20the%20team.%20If%20I%20were%20part%20of%20the%20management%2C%20I%20would%20definitely%20play%20him%20in%20the%20team%2C%20because%20we%20are%20all%20stakeholders%20of%20Indian%20cricket%20and%20we%20want%20the%20Indian%20Cricket%20Team%20to%20do%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarbhajan%20added%20that%20with%20Indian%20picking%20two%20left-arm%20spinners%2C%20one%20among%20them%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E)%20being%20an%20allrounder%2C%20and%20one%20Chinaman%20bowler%2C%20variety%20is%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20feel%20these%20two%20boys%2C%20they%20could%20have%20been%20very%20handy%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20and%20especially%20in%20conditions%20where%20they%20know%20what%20to%20do%20and%20how%20to%20take%20wickets.%20So%2C%20I%20believe%20these%20two%20guys%20are%20simply%20missed%20because%20we%20have%20selected%20two%20left-arm%20spinners%20who%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20play%20together%20in%20the%20same%20match%2C%20but%20Jadeja%20and%20Chahal%20could%20play%20in%20the%20same%20match%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20we%20have%20to%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20left-handers%2C%20then%20we%20need%20someone%20who%20can%20spin%20the%20ball%20outside%20as%20well.%20So%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20and%20Arshdeep%20should%20have%20been%20in%20the%20team%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20will%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20debate%20among%20everybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarbahajan%20Singh%20also%20said%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20be%20very%20strong%20in%20its%20batting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20believe%20batting%20is%20something%20that%20needs%20to%20come%20good%20because%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20batting%20since%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20It%20has%20been%20up%20and%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20a%20lot%20will%20depend%20on%20Rohit%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.c