cricket%20team's%20World%20Cup%202023%20is%20out.%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20squad%20announcement%20that%20this%20was%20the%20'best'%20side%20that%20they%20could%20chose%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Ftwo-people-missing-indias-world-cup-winning-stars-no-holds-barred-take-on-rohit-sharma-led-squad-4369638%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Ftwo-people-missing-indias-world-cup-winning-stars-no-holds-barred-take-on-rohit-sharma-led-squad-4369638%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Ftwo-people-missing-indias-world-cup-winning-stars-no-holds-barred-take-on-rohit-sharma-led-squad-4369638%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20'What%20Strategic%20Purpose%20Is%20Served%20by%20Changing%20Our%20Country%E2%80%99s%20Name%20to%20Bharat%3F'%20%7C%20Vivek%20Katju%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08143559%2FKT-8-Sep-.00_24_33_13.Still002.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20where%20he%20raises%20several%20serious%20issues%20that%20are%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20present%20debate%20over%20whether%20our%20country%E2%80%99s%20name%20should%20be%20India%20or%20Bharat%2C%20Vivek%20Katju%2C%20a%20former%20Ambassador%20to%20Afghanistan%20and%20Myanmar%2C%20has%20asked%20the%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20strategic%20purpose%20is%20served%20by%20changing%20our%20country%E2%80%99s%20name%20to%20Bharat%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20answering%20his%20own%20question%2C%20Katju%20points%20out%20that%20we%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20disturbing%20a%20happy%20equilibrium%20established%20over%20the%20last%2075%20years%20of%20using%20the%20name%20India%20in%20English%20and%20Bharat%20in%20Hindi.%20Using%20Bharat%20as%20the%20only%20name%20hereafter%20may%20well%20be%20acceptable%20to%20the%20Hindi-speaking%20states%20of%20north%20India%20but%20it%20could%20be%20objected%20to%20by%20states%20such%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20because%20they%20do%20not%20use%20the%20word%20Bharat%20but%20Bharatam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatju%20points%20out%20that%20language%20is%20an%20emotive%20issue%20and%20we%20have%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20seen%20political%20and%20social%20divisions%20over%20the%20politics%20of%20language.%20Those%20years%20or%20decades%20are%20happily%20behind%20us%2C%20so%20why%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20stirring%20trouble%20again%20and%20needlessly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Katju%20also%20explained%20that%20there%20were%20very%20good%20reasons%20why%20the%20founding%20fathers%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20embraced%20India.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20because%20they%20were%20fond%20of%20the%20name.%20It%20was%20because%20they%20wanted%20India%20to%20be%20recognised%20as%20the%20successor%20state%20to%20British%20India.%20As%20Katju%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CEven%20as%20a%20colony%20India%20had%20an%20international%20personality%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20our%20freedom%20movement%20wanted%20to%20retain%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20as%20the%20successor%20state%2C%20could%20immediately%20inherit%20membership%20of%20the%20UN%20(which%20had%20been%20obtained%20in%201945)%20and%20all%20the%20agreements%20and%20treaties%20signed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20the%20days%20when%20it%20was%20under%20British%20rule.%20That%20would%20not%20have%20been%20the%20case%20if%20our%20country%20had%20called%20itself%20Hindustan%20or%20Bharat.%20We%20would%20then%20not%20have%20been%20recognised%20as%20the%20successor%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20equally%20important%20point%2C%20Katju%20said%2C%20was%20that%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20was%20opposed%20to%20our%20country%20retaining%20the%20name%20India%20and%20insistent%20that%20we%20should%20be%20known%20as%20either%20Hindustan%20or%20Bharat.%20Had%20we%20called%20ourselves%20Bharat%20or%20Hindustan%20that%2C%20Katju%20adds%2C%20would%20have%20legitimised%20Jinnah%E2%80%99s%20two-nation%20theory.%20Instead%2C%20by%20retaining%20the%20name%20India%20we%20ensured%20that%20Pakistan%20is%20viewed%20as%20the%20seceding%20state.%20It%2C%20therefore%2C%20had%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20membership%20of%20the%20UN%20which%2C%20incidentally%2C%20Afghanistan%20opposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Katju%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tradition%20of%20using%20India%20in%20English%20and%20Bharat%20in%20Hindi%20is%20wise%20and%20constitutionally%20correct.%20Should%20its%20change%20be%20a%20priority%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%20Quite%20clearly%20his%20answer%20is%20no.%20We%20have%20many%20other%20challenges%20to%20contend%20with.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20unnecessarily%20add%20to%20them%20by%20disturbing%20the%20happy%20equilibrium%20of%20almost%20eight%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfX8gSR2WXSY%3Fsi%3DqZQSPEBuAXzprpq0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694164002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08143559%2FKT-8-Sep-.00_24_33_13.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwatch-what-strategic-purpose-is-served-by-changing-our-countrys-name-to-bharat-vivek-katju%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Katju%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tradition%20of%20using%20India%20in%20English%20and%20Bharat%20in%20Hindi%20is%20wise%20and%20constitutionally%20correct.%20Should%20its%20change%20be%20a%20prio