uot%3Bobviously%20special%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20joked%20about%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bson-in-law%20of%20India%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20first%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Indian%20heritage%20and%20married%20to%20an%20Indian%20-%20Akshata%20Murty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20a%20huddle%20on%20his%20flight%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20British%20Indian%20leader%20said%20he%20was%20excited%20to%20be%20back%20in%20India%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20country%20that%20is%20very%20near%20and%20dear%20to%20me%26quot%3B.%20He%20is%20joined%20on%20the%20visit%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Infosys%20co-founder%20Narayana%20Murthy%2C%20and%20is%20scheduled%20for%20bilateral%20talks%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20heading%20to%20the%20G20%20Summit%20with%20a%20clear%20focus.%20Stabilising%20the%20global%20economy.%20Building%20international%20relationships.%20Supporting%20the%20most%20vulnerable%2C%26quot%3B%20tweeted%20Rishi%20Sunak%20as%20he%20embarked%20on%20the%20three-day%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20obviously%20special.%20I%20saw%20somewhere%20that%20I%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20India's%20son-in-law%2C%20which%20I%20hope%20was%20meant%20affectionately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20travelling%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20has%20been%20flagged%20as%20a%20key%20topic%20on%20the%20agenda%20for%20the%20UK%20during%20the%20summit%20discussions%2C%20with%20Downing%20Street%20saying%20India's%20role%20and%20influence%20is%20%26quot%3Bvital%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20again%2C%20Vladimir%20Putin%20is%20failing%20to%20show%20his%20face%20at%20the%20G20.%20He%20is%20the%20architect%20of%20his%20own%20diplomatic%20exile%2C%20isolating%20himself%20in%20his%20presidential%20palace%20and%20blocking%20out%20criticism%20and%20reality.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20demonstrating%20that%20we%20will%20turn%20up%20and%20work%20together%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20pieces%20of%20Putin's%20destruction%2C%26quot%3B%20Rishi%20Sunak%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20Downing%20Street%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20UK%20will%20use%20%26quot%3Bevery%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20to%20show%20its%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20further%20foster%20global%20support%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20a%20vital%20role%20to%20play%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy%20in%20calling%20out%20Russia's%20assault%20on%20human%20rights%20and%20indeed%20democracy%20itself.%20We%20will%20use%20meetings%20with%20PM%20Modi%20or%20elsewhere%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20use%20that%20influence%20to%20bring%20an%20end%20to%20Putin's%20brutal%20invasion%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Sunak's%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-UK%20free%20trade%20agreement%20(FTA)%20negotiations%20are%20likely%20to%20also%20feature%20highly%20during%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-Rishi%20Sunak%20bilateral%20discussions%2C%20having%20just%20completed%2012%20rounds%20of%20negotiations%20but%20with%20no%20set%20timeframe%20for%20its%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20Downing%20Street%20has%20indicated%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20changes%20to%20the%20UK%20immigration%20policy%20as%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20though%20short-term%20business%20visas%20are%20up%20for%20discussion%20as%20part%20of%20the%20trade%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20UK%20government%20statistics%20peg%20the%20India-UK%20bilateral%20trade%20relationship%20as%20worth%20around%20GBP%2036%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20expected%20to%20be%20significantly%20enhanced%20with%20what%20both%20sides%20have%20branded%20as%20a%20deep%20and%20forward-looking%20FTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Sunak%20last%20met%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G7%20Summit%20in%20Hiroshima%