%20advancements%20on%20a%20global%20scale%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20literacy%20continues%20to%20pose%20substantial%20challenges.%20According%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Educational%2C%20Scientific%20and%20Cultural%20Organisation%20(UNESCO)%2C%20as%20of%202020%2C%20a%20staggering%20763%20million%20young%20individuals%20and%20adults%20in%20the%20world%20still%20lacked%20essential%20literacy%20skills.%20Recent%20crises%20-%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20climate%20change%20impacts%2C%20and%20conflicts%20-%20have%20only%20worsened%20the%20existing%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%2014th%20Session%20held%20in%20November%201966%2C%20UNESCO%20officially%20declared%20September%208%20as%20International%20Literacy%20Day%20(ILD).%20Since%20that%20time%2C%20most%20United%20Nations%20member%20states%20have%20consistently%20marked%20this%20date%20annually.%20The%20fundamental%20purpose%20of%20celebrating%20the%20ILD%20is%20to%20bolster%20public%20sentiment%20in%20favor%20of%20continuous%20efforts%20to%20combat%20illiteracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNESCO%20holds%20a%20central%20role%20in%20organizing%20International%20Literacy%20Day%20commemorations%2C%20which%20encompass%20worldwide%2C%20global%2C%20and%20regional%20levels%2C%20as%20well%20as%20events%20at%20the%20national%20and%20community%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20we%20celebrate%20International%20Literacy%20Day%2C%20let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20where%20India%20and%20its%20states%20stand%20in%20terms%20of%20literacy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20literacy%20rate%20among%20Indian%20women%20has%20witnessed%20significant%20progress%20over%20the%20years.%20In%20the%20early%20days%20of%20India's%20independence%2C%20a%20mere%20one%20out%20of%20eleven%20girls%2C%20approximately%20nine%20per%20cent%2C%20were%20literate%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20World%20Bank.%20Today%2C%20the%20literacy%20rate%20among%20women%20in%20India%20has%20surged%20to%2077%20per%20cent%2C%20whereas%20the%20male%20literacy%20rate%20stands%20at%2084.7%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20holds%20the%20lowest%20literacy%20rate%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20following%20closely%2C%20as%20stated%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education.%20According%20to%20the%20ministry%2C%20the%20literacy%20rate%20in%20rural%20India%20stands%20at%2067.77%20per%20cent%2C%20while%20in%20urban%20India%2C%20it%20is%2084.11%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Education%2C%20Annapurna%20Devi%2C%20shared%20this%20information%20in%20response%20to%20a%20written%20question%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20March%202023.%20She%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20scheme%20outlines%20a%20comprehensive%20educational%20continuum%2C%20spanning%20from%20pre-school%2C%20primary%2C%20upper%20primary%2C%20secondary%20to%20senior%20secondary%20levels.%20The%20central%20government%20supports%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20in%20implementing%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20to%20ensure%20universal%20access%20and%20retention%2C%20address%20gender%20and%20social%20category%20disparities%20in%20education%2C%20and%20enhance%20children's%20learning%20outcomes%20at%20all%20school%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20data%20shared%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Bihar%20has%20the%20lowest%20literacy%20rate%20at%2061.8%20per%20cent%2C%20followed%20by%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20at%2065.3%20per%20cent%20and%20Rajasthan%20at%2066.1%20per%20cent.%20Conversely%2C%20Kerala%20boasts%20the%20highest%20literacy%20rate%20at%2094%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20Lakshadweep%20at%2091.85%20per%20cent%20and%20Mizoram%20at%2091.33%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20adult%20literacy%20rates%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20ministry%20highlighted%20the%20centrally%20sponsored%20Saakshar%20Bharat%20scheme.%20This%20initiative%20was%20implemented%20in%20rural%20areas%20of%20404%20districts%20across%2026%20states%20and%20one%20Union%20Territory%2C%20targeting%20areas%20with%20adult%20female%20literacy%20rates%20of%2050%20per%20cent%20or%20lower%2C%20as%20per%20Census%202001%2C%20including%20districts%20affected%20by%20left-wing%20extremism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20was%20to%20increase%20the%20country's%20overall%20literacy%20rate%20to%2080%20per%20cent%20and%20reduce%20the%20gender%20gap%20to%2010%20percentage%20points%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20XII%20five-year%20plan.%20The%20scheme%20was%20extended%20until%20March%2031%2C%202018.%20During%20the%20Saakshar%20Bharat%20scheme's%20implementation%2C%20out%20of%20the%20total%20target%20of%20educating%207.00%20crore%20adult%20non-literates%2C%20approximately%207.64%20crore%20learners%20who%20successfully%20passed%20the%20biannual%20Basic%20Literacy%20Assessment%20Tests%20administered%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS)%20between%20August%202010%20and%20March%202018%20were%20certified%20as%20literate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20agencies%20and%20UNESCO's%20official%20website)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694161980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Foab8ocbo_college-education-generic_625x300_19_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Finternational-literacy-day-2023-know-about-remarkable-progress-made-by-india-4370870%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22To%20improve%20adult%20literacy%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20promoted%20the%20Saakshar%20Bharat%20scheme%20in%20404%20rural%20districts%20across%2026%20states%20and%20one%20Union%20Territory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Finternational-literacy-day-2023-know-about-remarkable-progress-made-by-india-4370870%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Finternational-literacy-day-