%2F103500824.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103500824.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThalpathy%20Vijay's%20next%20with%20Lokesh%20Kanagaraj%20called%20Leo%3A%20Bloody%20Sweet%20opened%20it's%20advance%20booking%20in%20UK%20and%20within%20first%2012%20hours%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20more%20than%205500%20tickets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fadvance-booking-for-thalapathy-vijays-leo-bloody-sweet-opens-in-uk%2Farticleshow%2F103500824.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Any%20Authoritarian%20State%20Has%20its%20Own%20Media%20Strategy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Myanmar%20Junta%20Is%20No%20Exception%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F11001834%2FProtest_in_Myanmar_against_Military_Coup_14-Feb-2021_02.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20text%20below%20is%20a%20slightly%20edited%20version%20of%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20to%20the%20M20%20Media%20Freedom%20Summit%20held%20online%20in%20Delhi%20on%20September%206%2C%202023%20by%20the%20M20%20Organising%20Committee%2C%20which%20comprises%2011%20editors%20from%20India%20and%20a%20former%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThank%20you%20so%20much%2C%20Siddharth.%20I%20am%20very%20pleased%20and%20very%20honoured%20to%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20this%20occasion%20to%20give%20a%20small%20talk.%20Just%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20this%20conference%20started%2C%20one%20of%20our%20journalists%20in%20Myanmar%20was%20sentenced%20to%2020%20years%20in%20jail.%20He%20was%20working%20underground%2C%20just%20covering%20the%20devastating%20cyclone%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20near%20to%20India%20actually.%20He%20was%20arrested%20and%20%3Cspan%3Ethen%20charged%20with%20so%20many%20kinds%20of%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20sedition%2C%20telecommunication%20laws%2C%20defamation%20%E2%80%93%20all%20these%20but%20without%20any%20hearing.%20He%20was%20tried%2C%20just%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20in%20a%20military%20tribunal%20and%20they%20handed%20out%2020%20years%20of%20prison%20sentence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20situation%20facing%20the%20media%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar%20is%20right%20between%20India%20and%20China%20and%20north%20of%20Thailand%2C%20actually.%20We%20are%20located%20in%20a%20very%20strategic%20geopolitical%20belt%20but%20because%20of%20the%20insignificance%20of%20our%20country%2C%20I%20think%20we%20did%20not%20manage%20to%20attract%20a%20lot%20of%20international%20attention%20after%20the%20military%20coup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%2045%20years%20old%20and%20this%20is%20the%20worst%20situation%20we%20have%20ever%20witnessed%20in%20our%20lifetime.%20What%20I%20want%20to%20say%20is%2C%20that%20we%20have%2021st-century%20jet%20fighters%20making%20daily%20bombardments%20on%20rural%20villagers%20and%20thousands%20of%20people%20were%20incarcerated%20including%20dozens%20of%20journalists.%20For%20example%2C%20after%20the%20military%20coup%2C%20they%20raided%20our%20offices%20and%20also%20confiscated%20our%20houses%20and%20they%20chased%20down%20even%20the%20immediate%20family%20members%20of%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20want%20to%20say%20is%20that%20Myanmar%2C%20as%20a%20neighbouring%20country%20of%20India%2C%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20country%20very%20similar%20to%20North%20Korea%20in%20terms%20of%20repression%20and%20brutality.%20A%20lot%20of%20brutalities%20are%20going%20on%20but%20just%20because%20of%20the%20insignificance%20of%20our%20country%20on%20a%20geopolitical%20scale%2C%20we%20do%20not%20manage%20to%20attract%20a%20lot%20of%20attention.%20I%20want%20to%20request%20my%20colleagues.%20It%E2%80%99s%20very%20difficult%20to%20collect%20news%20and%20information%20but%20I%20want%20to%20request%20all%20my%20colleagues%20in%20the%20media%20industry%20around%20the%20world%20to%20be%20able%20to%20give%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20attention%20to%20what%E2%80%99s%20going%20on%20in%20our%20country.%20You%20know%2C%20you%20cannot%20even%20go%20out%20with%20a%20camera%20in%20our%20country%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22On%20Paper%2C%20Journalists%20in%20South%20Africa%20Are%20Free%20to%20Do%20Their%20Work.%20But%20Attacks%20Say%20Otherwise%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fsouth-africa-media-journalists-attacks-freedom-m20%5C%22%3EOn%20Paper%2C%20Journalists%20in%20South%20Africa%20Are%20Free%20to%20Do%20Their%20Work.%20But%20Attacks%20Say%20Otherwise%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20challenges%20facing%20us.%20The%20first%20challenge%20is%20the%20obvious%20repression%2C%20the%20second%20is%20financial%20constraint.%20We%20cannot%20generate%20any%20kind%20of%20revenue%20because%20we%20are%20already%20outlawed.%20All%20the%20local%20businesses%20will%20not%20want%20to%20advertise%20with%20any%20outlawed%20organisation.%20We%20receive%20a%20bit%20of%20money%2C%20sometimes%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20money%2C%20from%20certain%20governments%20like%20the%20US.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20circumstantial.%20A%20lot%20of%20contractors%20in%20the%20name%20of%20media%20development%2C%20just%20see%20us%20as%20pawns%20for%20the%20causes%20for%20revenue%20generation%2C%20just%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20development%20assistance%20is%20coming%20to%20travel%20to%20countries%20like%20ours%20in%20the%20name%20of%20media%20development%20but%20much%20of%20the%20money%20actually%20going%20to%20the%20intermediary%20media%20development%20organisations%20based%20in%20Europe%20or%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20We%20will%20receive%20only%20a%20small%20check.%20If%20you%20give%20one%20million%20dollars%20to%20all%20these%20media%20outlets%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20they%20will%20receive%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20or%20maybe%20ten%20thousand%20dollars%20at%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20only%20receive%20a%20very%20small%20percentage%20of%20direct%20support.%20These%20media%20organisations%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20do%20anything.%20They%20will%20just%20write%20contracts%2C%20and%20ask%20us%20to%20report%20on%20monitoring.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20do%20anything%20but%20they%20will%20give%20us%20the%20impression%20that%20they%20are%20working%20full-time.%20We%20are%20in%20a%20really%20tough%20financial%20situation.%20We%20cannot%20make%20any%20sort%20of%20business%2C%20we%20cannot%20get%20any%20proper%20support%20from%20international%20development%20etc.%20But%20I%20feel%20really%20grateful%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20that%20the%20US%2C%20the%20biggest%20country%2C%20is%20consistently%20supporting%20the%20media%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20I%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20is%20that%20any%20authoritarian%20state%20has%20their%20own%20media%20strategy.%20They%20will%20hire%20lobby%20groups%20in%20the%20US%20or%20in%20Europe%20etc.%20Now%2C%20in%20our%20country%2C%20the%20military%20has%20been%20reaching%20out.%20They%20have%20formed%20their%20own%20press%20council%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fake%20press%20council.%20Using%20this%20vehicle%2C%20they%20will%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Indian%20Press%20Council%2C%20they%20will%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Japanese%20Council%20and%20then%20in%20most%20cases%20they%20will%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20former%20chairman%20or%20the%20acting%20chairman%20of%20the%20press%20council%20and%20spread%20propaganda%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20what%20happened%20two%20months%20ago.%20They%20invited%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Japanese%20Foreign%20Correspondent%20Club%20to%20Myanmar.%20They%20just%20gave%20propaganda%20interviews.%20They%20would%20even%20share%20breaking%20news%20between%20Aung%20San%20Suu%20Kyi%20and%20the%20Thai%20foreign%20minister.%20And%20a%20so-called%20journalist%20at%20the%20Japanese%20Foreign%20Correspondent%20Club%2C%20he%20has%20a%20small%20website%2C%20where%20he%20would%20write%20all%20these%20news%20pieces%2C%20and%20propagate%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20thing%20happened%20the%20India.%20They%20have%20invited%20the%20Indian%20chairman%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Correspondent%20Club%20to%20Myanmar%2C%20etc.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fforeign-correspondents-club-members-resign-after-president-visits-myanmar-meets-junta-ministers%5C%22%3EThere%20was%20some%20sort%20of%20backlash%20in%20India%20as%20well%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20junta%20is%20doing%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%20to%20misinform%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20our%20country.%20So%2C%20I%20really%20want%20to%20request%20you%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20this%20situation%20as%20well.%20Thank%20you%20very%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESwe%20Win%20is%20editor%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EMyanmar%20Now%3Cem%3E%2C%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694161228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F11001834%2FProtest_in_Myanmar_against_Military_Coup_14-Feb-2021_02.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fm20-myanmar-junta-media-journalists%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20media%20needs%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20Myanmar%2C%20even%20though%20we%20are%20not%20significant%20geopolitically.%20The%20country's%20media%20cannot%20generate%20any%20kind%20of%20revenue%20because%20we%20are%20already%20outlawed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fm20-myanmar-junta-media-journalists%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Twitterati%20