0coast%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20with%20two%20pilots%20now%20missing%2C%20authorities%20said%20on%20Friday.%20The%20crash%20happened%20offshore%2C%20though%20the%20UAE's%20General%20Civil%20Aviation%20Authorities%20did%20not%20specify%20where.%20It%20identified%20the%20aircraft%20involved%20as%20a%20Bell%20212%2C%20which%20can%20carry%2014%20passengers%20and%20a%20pilot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fa-helicopter-crashes-off-the-united-arab-emirates-coast-2-pilots-are-missing%2Farticleshow%2F103499657.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fa-helicopter-crashes-off-the-united-arab-emirates-coast-2-pilots-are-missing%2Famp_articleshow%2F103499657.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fa-helicopter-crashes-off-the-united-arab-emirates-coast-2-pilots-are-missing%2Famp_articleshow%2F103499657.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Distributing%20The%20Bible%2C%20Encouraging%20Education%20Not%20%E2%80%98Allurement%E2%80%99%20for%20Conversion%3A%20Allahabad%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F24132319%2FAllahabad_high_court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20(September%206)%20that%20distributing%20the%20%3Cem%3EBible%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20encouraging%20children%20to%20get%20educated%20and%20providing%20%E2%80%98good%20teachings%E2%80%99%20do%20not%20amount%20to%20%E2%80%98allurement%E2%80%99%20under%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20unlawful%20conversion%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Shamim%20Ahmed%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2Fjose-papachen-and-another-vs-state-of-up-thru-prin-secy-home-lko-and-another-2023-livelaw-ab-310-criminal-appeal-no-877-of-2023-allahabad-high-court-490919.pdf%5C%22%3Eorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20hearing%20an%20appeal%20by%20Jose%20Papachen%20and%20Sheeja%20against%20the%20rejection%20of%20their%20bail%20plea%20back%20in%20March%20this%20year%20by%20a%20special%20judge%20for%20cases%20relating%20to%20the%20SC%2FST%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPapachen%20and%20Sheeja%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20alluring%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities%20into%20converting%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20counsel%20said%20they%20have%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20January%2024%2C%20the%20same%20day%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20filed%20against%20them%20under%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202021%20and%20the%20Schedule%20Caste%20and%20Schedule%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20against%20them%20in%20a%20police%20station%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20district%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20one%20Zila%20Manti%2C%20who%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.upvidhai.gov.in%2FMediaGallery%2F3of2021.pdf%5C%22%3EProhibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20makes%20it%20illegal%20to%20convert%20someone%20by%20way%20of%20%E2%80%98allurement%E2%80%99%20(among%20other%20things).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20defines%20allurement%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Coffer%20of%20temptation%20in%20the%20form%20of%20any%20gift%2C%20gratification%2C%20easy%20money%20or%20material%20benefit%20%E2%80%A6%20employment%2C%20free%20education%20in%20%5Ba%5D%20reputed%20school%20run%20by%20any%20religious%20body%3B%20or%20better%20lifestyle%2C%20divine%20displeasure%20or%20otherwise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20in%20the%20case%20alleged%20that%20Papachen%20and%20Sheeja%20used%20%E2%80%9Cpsychological%20pressure%20for%20forceful%20conversions%20as%20part%20of%20their%20plan%20to%20set%20up%20%5Ba%20Christian%20state%5D%E2%80%9D%20and%20allured%20people%20by%20%E2%80%9Cundue%20influence%E2%80%9D%20to%20convert%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20recorded%20Zila%20Manti%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20that%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities%20who%20Papachen%20and%20Sheeja%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20convert%20became%20%E2%80%9Cannoyed%E2%80%9D%20by%20their%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%5C%22%3ENo%20Country%20for%20Religious%20Converts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20villagers%20in%20question%20gave%20their%20statements%2C%20which%20were%20recorded%20during%20their%20police%20examination%20as%20witnesses%2C%20saying%20that%20Papachen%20and%20Sheeja%20%E2%80%9Cused%20to%20give%20them%20good%20teachings%20%E2%80%A6%20distribute%20%3Cem%3EHoly%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EBible%3C%2Fem%3E%20books%20to%20them%20%E2%80%A6%20%5Band%5D%20encourage%20them%20to%20get%20their%20children%20educated%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20instructed%20them%20not%20to%20fight%20and%20consume%20alcohol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20these%20statements%2C%20the%20court%20ruled%20that%20these%20activities%20did%20not%20constitute%20allurement%20under%20UP%E2%80%99s%20unlawful%20conversion%20law%20and%20granted%20bail%20to%20Papachen%20and%20Sheeja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Justice%20Ahmed%20also%20noted%20that%20under%20the%20section%20of%20this%20law%20concerning%20allurement%2C%20only%20the%20aggrieved%20person(s)%20or%20their%20relatives%20can%20lodge%20a%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20Further%20considering%20that%20the%20complainant%20is%20Zila%20Mantri%20of%20a%20ruling%20party%20and%20is%20neither%20the%20aggrieved%20person%2C%20his%2Fher%20parents%2C%20brother%2C%20sister%20or%20any%20other%20person%2C%20who%20is%20related%20to%20him%2Fher%20by%20blood%2C%20marriage%20or%20adoption%2C%20as%20provided%20under%20Section%204%20of%20the%20%5BUnlawful%20Conversion%20Act%5D%2C%20thus%20the%20complainant%20is%20not%20competent%20to%20lodge%20the%20present%20FIR%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%E2%80%99s%20legislature%20enacted%20the%20unlawful%20conversion%20law%20in%202020%20as%20an%20ordinance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-56330206%5C%22%3Ein%20response%20to%20what%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20calls%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20also%20criminalises%20marriages%20done%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Csole%20purpose%20of%20unlawful%20conversion%20or%20vice%20versa%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20used%20multiple%20times%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20to%20stop%20consenting%20inter-faith%20couples%20from%20being%20together%20and%20getting%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight-wing%20Hindu%20vigilantes%20have%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20disrupting%20these%20marriages%2C%20and%20several%20Muslim%20men%20have%20faced%20jail%20time%20even%20when%20their%20partners%20have%20made%20clear%20that%20they%20consented%20to%20the%20relationship%20and%20were%20not%20forced%20to%20convert.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694158257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F24132319%2FAllahabad_high_court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdistributing-bibles-encouraging-childrens-education-not-allurement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20complainant%20in%20the%20case%20was%20a%20BJP%20member%20bearing%20no%20relation%20to%20the%20accused%2C%20who%20spent%20over%20seven%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20UP'