om%20of%20speech%2C%20freedom%20of%20thought%20and%20all%20these%20things.%20You%20know%2C%20Korea%20has%20sort%20of%20enjoyed%20over%20the%20past%2020%20or%2025%20years%20more%20or%20less%2C%20a%20pretty%20good%20freedom%20of%20speech%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20the%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%E2%80%99s%20revelation%20that%20some%20group%20%E2%80%93%20they%20call%20themselves%20%E2%80%9Cjournalists.%E2%80%9D%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20they%20are%20but%20some%20of%20these%20people%20are%20using%2C%20not%20the%20mainstream%20media%20but%20some%20sort%20of%20an%20ad%20hoc%20propaganda%20type%20media.%20There%20was%20a%20cartel%20of%20people%20including%20the%20then%20ruling%20party%20members.%20The%20ruling%20party%20introduced%20the%20ad%20hoc-propaganda%20type%20of%20the%20new%20service%20that%20caters%20to%20a%20leftist%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20gathered%20up%20with%20the%20so-called%20established%20media%20institutions%20that%20sympathised%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%20at%20that%20time%20and%20the%20politicians%20from%20the%20ruling%20party.%20This%20all%20happened%20like%2018%20months%20ago.%20They%20all%20tried%20to%20create%20something%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20true%20at%20all.%20They%20were%20trying%20to%20create%20this%20phenomenon%20to%20influence%20the%20presidential%20election%20and%20to%20discredit%20one%20of%20the%20main%20contenders%20in%20the%20presidential%20campaign.%20Now%20it%20is%20being%20revealed%20that%20somebody%20paid%20off%20somebody%20and%20then%20they%20had%20a%20falsified%20interview%20claiming%20that%20this%20presidential%20candidate%20was%20illegally%20covering%20up%20some%20investigations%20and%20so%20on.%20This%20thing%20was%20reiterated%20through%20established%20news%20print%20media%20as%20well%20as%20some%20of%20the%20mainstream%20broadcasting%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjapan-china-press-m20%5C%22%3EJapanese%20Media%20Needs%20to%20Learn%20How%20to%20Report%20on%20National%20Security%20%E2%80%93%20Especially%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%20is%20becoming%20a%20big%20scandal%20because%2C%20we%20suspected%20that%20there%20would%20be%20some%20connections%20here%20and%20there%2C%20but%20now%20it%20is%20becoming%20evident%20that%20all%20these%20people%20are%20connected%20somehow%20and%20some%20guy%20even%20paid%20off%20somebody.%20Now%20the%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%20is%20investigating%20journalists%20who%20carried%20out%20these%20stories%20in%20these%20established%20broadcasting%20companies%20without%20carrying%20the%20voices%20of%20those%20who%20said%20that%20this%20was%20not%20true%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20evident%20that%20this%20person%20who%20was%20a%20witness%20kept%20on%20telling%20the%20truth%20that%20this%20person%20didn%E2%80%99t%20cover%20anything%20up%2C%20%E2%80%98didn%E2%80%99t%20approach%20me%E2%80%99%20or%20whatever.%20But%20these%20established%20news%20organisations%20never%20carried%20his%20story%20and%20only%20carried%20the%20fabricated%20stories%20in%20mainstream%20news%20media.%20So%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20afraid%20that%20the%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%20will%20start%20investigating%20journalists%20who%20collaborated%20in%20this%20fabrication%20of%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20thing%20is%20about%20this%20fake%20news.%20These%20established%20news%20organisations%20like%20KBS%2C%20NBC%2C%20JTBC%2C%20these%20broadcasting%20companies%20and%20these%20two%20print%20media%20like%20%3Cem%3EKyunghyang%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20and%20%3Cem%3EHankyoreh%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper.%20These%20five%20established%20newspapers%20went%20along%20with%20fake%20news%20without%20substantiating%20the%20stories.%20Whether%20you%E2%80%99re%20left%20or%20right%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you%E2%80%99re%20writing%20with%20your%20facts%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter.%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20conservative%20newspaper%20or%20leftist%20newspaper%20as%20long%20as%20the%20journalist%20is%20writing%20stories%20based%20on%20facts%20and%20criticising%20opinions%2C%20all%20that%20is%20acceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20government%20to%20come%20and%20start%20investigating%20our%20colleagues%2C%20whether%20you%E2%80%99re%20left%20or%20right%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter.%20You%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%20coming%20and%20investigating%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELo%20and%20behold%2C%20because%20these%20established%20newspapers%20carried%20out%20these%20fake%20news%2C%20blatantly%2C%20without%20substantiating%20the%20story%20and%20even%20fabricating%20the%20witness%E2%80%99s%20account%20for%20their%20political%20cause%2C%20it%20is%20a%20sad%20story%20that%20the%20prosecutor%E2%80%99s%20office%20will%20come%20after%20these%20journalists%20and%20check%20their%20accounts%20if%20they%20received%20money%20and%20so%20on.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20accounts%2C%20a%20former%20journalist%20of%20a%20major%20established%20newspaper%20went%20into%20the%20labour%20union%20newspaper.%20This%20guy%20received%20%24%20130%2C%20000%20for%20fabricating%20the%20story%20as%20it%20turned%20out.%20It%E2%80%99s%20going%20wild.%20This%20is%20the%20most%20serious%20incident%20that%E2%80%99s%20happening%20right%20now%20in%20the%20Korean%20media%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99m%20just%20reporting%20to%20you%20as%20it%20is%20happening%20right%20now.%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20afraid%20that%20we%20journalists%20including%20these%20established%20newspapers%20or%20established%20news%20media%20leaning%20on%20the%20left%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20fine%20%E2%80%93%20they%20wrote%20and%20ran%20fabricated%20stories%2C%20without%20substation%2C%20shading%20all%20the%20actual%20things%20with%20massive%20factual%20errors%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20being%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fm20-media-everywhere-face-four-common-challenges-a-coalition-is-the-best-way-to-deal-with-them%5C%22%3EM20%3A%20Media%20Everywhere%20Face%20Four%20Common%20Challenges%2C%20a%20Coalition%20Is%20the%20Best%20Way%20to%20Deal%20With%20Them%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20Should%20I%20protest%20to%20the%20government%2C%20%E2%80%98Please%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%20because%20these%20journalists%20clearly%20screwed%20things%20up%3F%E2%80%99%20They%20royally%20messed%20up%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20excusable%20thing.%20We%20are%20not%20so%20sure%20what%20to%20do%20at%20the%20moment%20except%20just%20watch%20how%20this%20investigation%20turns%20out.%20But%20the%20real%20proof%20is%20that%20one%20guy%20paid%20off%20%24%20130%2C000%20to%20this%20guy%20who%20fabricated%20the%20story.%20Then%2C%20the%20five%20established%20news%20media%20just%20carried%20all%20these%20stories%20repeatedly%2C%20three%20days%20before%20the%20election%2C%20clearly%20aiming%20to%20discredit%20the%20other%20presidential%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20big%20mess.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20clean%20things%20up.%20We%20just%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20how%20the%20actual%20thing%20really%20happened%20back%2018%20months%20ago.%20We%E2%80%99re%20just%20waiting%20to%20see%20how%20it%20all%20gonna%20play.%20This%20is%20the%20big%20situation%20right%20now%20in%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20that%2C%20another%20issue%20that%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20raise%20with%20you%20is%20that%20the%20media%20industry%20in%20Korea%2C%20just%20as%20in%20the%20US%20or%20anywhere%20else%2C%20is%20very%2C%20very%20polarised.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20handful%20of%20conservative%20newspapers%20and%20then%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20handful%20of%20progressive%20leftist%20newspapers%20and%20there%20is%20a%20group%20of%20YouTubers%20in%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasically%2C%20the%20newspapers%20are%20free%20but%20not%20really.%20They%20are%20regulated%20by%20the%20government%20except%20that%20you%20have%20to%20register%20as%20a%20print%20agency.%20The%20broadcasters%20are%20regulated%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other%20by%20the%20government%20but%20you%20know%20relatively%20they%20maintain%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%20do.%20But%20YouTubers%20or%20freelance%20SNS%20%5Bsocial%20media%5D%20influencers%20claiming%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cjournalists%E2%80%9D%20asserting%20things%20that%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20are%20not%20substantiated.%20They%20are%20polarising%20the%20political%20environment%20in%20Korea%20and%20probably%20this%20is%20true%20with%20all%20your%20countries%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20question%20to%20you%20is%20what%20shall%20we%20do%20with%20these%20people%3F%20Shall%20we%2C%20you%20know%2C%20try%20to%20educate%20them%3F%20We%20try%20to%20tell%20them%20not%20to%20do%20it%20that%20way.%20We%20have%20to%20maintain%20the%20need%20to%20do%20things%20based%20on%20facts%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20SNS%20people%20start%20making%20rambunctious%20claims%20then%20later%20on%20they%20go%20to%20jail.%20Before%20they%20go%20to%20jail%2C%20they%20argue%20about%20freedom%20of%20speech.%20Our%20big%20dilemma%20is%20whether%20these%20people%20should%20be%20protected%20based%20on%20this%20freedom%20of%20speech%20when%20they%20are%20making%20totally%20absurd%2C%20fabricated%2C%20rambunctious%20stories%20or%20shall%20we%20still%20protect%20these%20people%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20of%20opinion.%20The%20reason%20I%E2%80%99ve%20mentioned%20this%20is%20because%20of%20the%20big%20scandal%20right%20now%20that%20we%20are%20facing%20today%20in%20the%20Korean%20media%20stems%20from%20precisely%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20established%20media%20used%20these%20so-called%20media%20that%20are%20untouched%20by%20the%20government%20regulation%20or%20not%20considered%20as%20estab