20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20get%20the%20good%20copyright%20deals%20from%20Google%2C%20other%20social%20media%2C%20or%20big%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20question%20is%20maybe%20something%20unique%20in%20Japan%20because%20that%20is%20something%20we%20are%2C%20especially%20I%20am%2C%20facing%20every%20day%20%E2%80%93%20how%20to%20report%20about%20the%20national%20security%20issues%2C%20which%20we%20have%20not%20focused%20on%20so%20much%20in%20the%20past.%20That%20is%20about%20how%20to%20report%20on%20China.%20As%20you%20know%20that%20China%20has%20expanded%20so%20much%20and%20it%20is%20quite%20the%20threat%20from%20the%20Japanese%20standpoint.%20This%20is%20of%20course%20affecting%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20Japanese%20media%20coverage.%20I%20would%20say%2C%20since%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20II%20and%20especially%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20we%20have%20been%20living%20in%20a%20very%20peaceful%20regional%20and%20international%20environment%20so%20we%20have%20not%20faced%20this%20kind%20of%20problem%20of%20how%20to%20report%20this%20possible%20strife%20which%20is%20now%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20government%20has%20its%20strengths%20and%20its%20defence%20budget%20and%20a%20modernised%20defence%20doctrine.%20The%20trend%20is%20that%20Japanese%20government%20policy%20and%20public%20opinion%20about%20China%20are%20getting%20worse%20and%20worse.%20Those%20conditions%20inevitably%20and%20naturally%20affect%20the%20course%20and%20overtone%20of%20the%20media%20coverage%20of%20Japan.%20We%2C%20especially%20journalists%2C%20know%20that%20we%20have%20to%20make%20much%20more%20nuanced%20stories%2C%20including%20many%20faces%2C%20and%20many%20aspects%20of%20China%2C%20which%20sometimes%20we%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fm20-media-everywhere-face-four-common-challenges-a-coalition-is-the-best-way-to-deal-with-them%5C%22%3EM20%3A%20Media%20Everywhere%20Face%20Four%20Common%20Challenges%2C%20a%20Coalition%20Is%20the%20Best%20Way%20to%20Deal%20With%20Them%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20sometimes%20it%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20very%20friendly%20and%20familiar%20space%20for%20the%20Japanese%2C%20but%20most%20of%20the%20cases%20nowadays%20are%20about%20the%20threat%20from%20China.%20Especially%20after%20the%20release%20of%20the%20contaminated%20or%20I%20would%20say%20treated%20water%20from%20the%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20power%20plants%20and%20that%20is%20a%20big%20issue%20in%20this%20region.%20China%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20release%20of%20the%20water%20but%20without%20clear%20evidence%20from%20the%20scientific%20standpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20we%20concretely%20had%20some%20kind%20of%20conclusion%20that%20China%20is%20acting%20against%20or%20opposing%20whatever%20Japan%20does%2C%20without%20a%20point%20of%20negotiation.%20With%20that%20kind%20of%20attitude%20of%20China%2C%20the%20Japanese%20public%20is%20very%20strongly%20opposed%20to%20China%2C%20especially%20the%20part%20of%20the%20question%20of%20international%20or%20national%20security%20reporting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20Japan%20are%20maybe%20a%20different%20case.%20People%20in%20the%20defence%20department%2C%20foreign%20ministry%20or%20national%20security%20office%20of%20the%20Japanese%20government%20say%20this%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20secret%20information%20and%20that%20is%20why%20they%20cannot%20disclose%20all%20the%20information.%20And%20so%20that%20information%20to%20media%20people%20like%20me%20leads%20to%20reporting%20which%20in%20most%20of%20the%20cases%20is%20not%20based%20on%20some%20kind%20of%20fact%20or%20first-hand%20information%20of%20Chinese%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20very%20hard%20job%20for%20us%20because%20we%20know%20that%20we%20have%20to%20put%20in%20much%20more%20effort%20from%20various%20angles.%20Most%20of%20the%20reporting%20is%20very%20one-sided%20which%20is%20a%20very%20nationalistic%20and%20sometimes%20chauvinistic%20and%20militaristic.%20I%20think%20that%20our%20reports%20are%20not%20well%20qualified%20at%20this%20time%2C%20which%20sees%20a%20very%20difficult%20situation%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20problem%20is%20with%20recruiting%20future%20journalists%20from%20colleges%20or%20universities%20in%20Japan.%20Most%20of%20those%20talented%2C%20young%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20choose%20journalism%20as%20a%20vocation%20or%20as%20a%20profession.%20They%20like%20to%20go%20to%20the%20banking%20sector%20or%20consulting%20sector%20or%20trade%20companies.%20They%20say%20journalism%20is%20very%20hard%20and%20that%20kind%20of%20a%20job%20does%20not%20make%20enough%20money%20for%20them%20so%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20they%20try%20to%20get%20into%20other%20sectors.%20That%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20situation%20in%20Japanese%20media.%20We%20need%20to%20generate%20good%20and%20talented%20young%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20I%20think%20that%20those%20youngsters%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20the%20media%20have%20started%20doing%20some%20kind%20of%20non-profit%20journalism%20in%20Japan.%20They%20are%20actually%20young%20people%20and%20financed%20by%20crowdfunding%20the%20organisation%2C%20so%20they%20are%20not%20affected%20by%20commercial%20companies.%20So%20they%20are%20much%20more%20likely%20to%20challenge%20authorities%2C%20which%20our%20traditional%20media%20has%20refrained%20from%20doing.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20that%20this%20is%20kind%20of%20a%20positive%20sign%20of%20Japanese%20journalism.%20We%20see%20that%20we%20are%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20transformation%20or%20transit.%20Sometimes%2C%20you%20know%2C%20changing%20the%20media%20culture%20from%20the%20traditional%20media%20to%20the%20new%20media%20is%20something%20I%20take%20some%20hope%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ll%20stop%20here.%2