of%20Largest%20Bloc%20of%20Global%20South%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F03233115%2FFu5WdfyWwAA2CWl.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%2C%20while%20claiming%20to%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20during%20its%20G20%20presidency%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20scale%20down%20its%20participation%20at%20the%20summit%20of%20the%20largest%20alliance%20of%20developing%20countries%20by%20cancelling%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20to%20Cuba%20next%20week.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20September%2015%20to%2016%2C%20the%20Cuban%20capital%20of%20Havana%20will%20host%20a%20rare%20summit%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98G-77%20plus%20China%E2%80%99%20grouping%2C%20for%20which%20invitations%20had%20been%20sent%20out%20to%20heads%20of%20states%20of%20members%20and%20their%20ministers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormed%20in%201964%2C%20the%20group%20has%20increased%20its%20size%20over%20the%20years%20and%20currently%20has%20134%20developing%20nations%20as%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20group%E2%80%99s%20importance%20is%20especially%20noted%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20where%20it%20is%20the%20largest%20bloc%20of%20countries%20with%20a%20rotating%20presidency.%20India%20had%20been%20the%20first%20president%20of%20the%20G-77%20in%20New%20York.%20China%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20group%2C%20but%20often%20aligns%20politically%20with%20the%20group%2C%20so%20official%20statements%20at%20various%20multilateral%20platforms%20are%20often%20labelled%20%E2%80%98G-77%20plus%20China%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20it%20is%20a%20loose%20association%2C%20summits%20at%20a%20high%20political%20level%2C%20such%20as%20that%20in%20Havana%20%E2%80%93%20that%20will%20see%20participation%20at%20the%20level%20of%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%20and%20foreign%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20rare%20occurrence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20was%20earlier%20confirmed%20to%20be%20leading%20the%20delegation%20to%20Cuba.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%2C%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20left%2C%20his%20visit%20has%20been%20cancelled.%20The%20official%20reason%20is%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20that%20has%20been%20convened%20by%20the%20government%20from%20September%2018%2C%20for%20which%20the%20presence%20of%20all%20government%20ministers%20has%20been%20made%20mandatory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20it%20had%20taken%20place%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20first%20visit%20to%20Cuba%20since%20taking%20over%20as%20foreign%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20special%20session%20seems%20to%20have%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20as%20Jaishankar%20too%20had%20publicly%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20be%20travelling%20to%20Cuba.%20In%20a%20speech%20at%20the%20CII%20India-LAC%20conclave%20on%20August%203%2C%20Jaishankar%20was%20speaking%20about%20his%20travels%20to%20the%20region%20and%20revealed%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20I%20expect%20next%20month%20to%20be%20in%20Cuba%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20reported%20by%20the%20state%20Cuban%20news%20agency%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prensa-latina.cu%2F2023%2F08%2F03%2Fanuncia-canciller-de-india-visita-a-cuba-en-septiembre%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPrensa%20Latina%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20noted%20that%20the%20Indian%20minister%20was%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Group%20of%2077%20plus%20China%E2%80%99%20summit%20on%20September%2015%20and%2016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20Indian%20delegation%20would%20now%20be%20led%20by%20MEA%20secretary%20(west)%20Sanjay%20Varma.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20foreign%20minister%E2%80%99s%20high-level%20presence%20at%20the%20Cuba%20summit%20could%20have%20pushed%20forward%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20claim%20to%20that%20it%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fg20-how-india-emerged-as-the-voice-of-global-south%2Farticleshow%2F103410416.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evoice%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Global%20South%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20especially%20since%20the%20gathering%20in%20Cuba%20comes%20within%20a%20week%20of%20India%20hosting%20the%20G20%20summit.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20its%20presidency%20in%20G20%2C%20India%20has%20positioned%20its%20term%20as%20that%20which%20will%20bring%20this%20%E2%80%98voice%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20south%20to%20the%20table%20for%20shaping%20global%20economic%20and%20monetary%20policies.%20%E2%80%9COur%20G20%20priorities%20will%20be%20shaped%20in%20consultation%20with%20not%20just%20our%20G20%20partners%20but%20also%20our%20fellow-travellers%20in%20the%20global%20south%2C%20whose%20voice%20often%20goes%20unheard%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fet-commentary%2Findias-g20-presidency-to-usher-in-human-centric-globalisation-writes-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F95893782.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%20PM%20Modi%20on%20December%201%2C%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Washington-based%20Council%20for%20Foreign%20Relations%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfr.org%2Fblog%2Fwhat-expect-indias-g20-summit%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobserved%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Indian%20PM%20%E2%80%9Csees%20the%20G20%20presidency%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20India%E2%80%99s%20credentials%20as%20a%20bridge%20between%20Global%20South%20countries%20and%20the%20West%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20buttress%20this%20point%2C%20India%20even%20held%20a%20virtual%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2Fvoice-of-global-summit.htm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DVoice%2520of%2520Global%2520South%2520Summit%2520has%2520been%2520India%2527s%2520endeavour%2520to%2Caddressing%2520the%2520concerns%2520and%2520priorities.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVoice%20of%20Global%20South%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20meeting%20in%20January%20where%20ministers%20and%20officials%20from%20around%20the%20world%20were%20asked%20to%20present%20their%20priorities%20that%20could%20be%20used%20as%20inputs%20for%20the%20G20%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20article%20published%20in%20various%20international%20papers%20on%20September%207%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20wrote%20about%20the%20importance%20given%20by%20India%20to%20developing%20countries.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20December%202022%2C%20when%20we%20took%20over%20the%20presidency%20from%20Indonesia%2C%20I%20wrote%20that%20a%20mindset%20shift%20must%20be%20catalysed%20by%20the%20G20.%20This%20was%20especially%20needed%20in%20the%20context%20of%20mainstreaming%20the%20marginalised%20aspirations%20of%20developing%20countries%2C%20the%20Global%20South%20and%20Africa%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20also%20described%20the%20%E2%80%98Voice%20of%20Global%20South%E2%80%99%20summit%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20foremost%20initiatives%20under%20our%20presidency%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20further%20boasted%20that%20his%20presidency%20will%20see%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20ever%20participation%20from%20African%20countries%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20it%20witnessed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg20-likely-to-become-g21-with-induction-of-african-union%5C%22%3Epush%20for%20inclusion%20of%20African%20Union%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20G20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694153549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F03233115%2FFu5WdfyWwAA2CWl.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg77-plus-china-global-south-voice-india-cancel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20start%20of%20its%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20India%20has%20positioned%20itself%20as%20the%20'voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South'.%20But%20now%20it%20has%20cited%20the%20special%20parliament%20session%20as%20reason%20why%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20cannot%20travel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg77-plus-china-global-south-voice-india-cancel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Dalit%20Students'%20Suicides%20in%20Two%20Months%20Highlight%20'Institutionalised%20Discrimination'%20at%20IITs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13134317%2FIIT_Delhi_Entrance.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20to%20you%2C%20I%20am%20under%20radar%20of%20the%20faculty%20after%20the%20recent%20suicide%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20BTech%20student%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Delhi%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20suicide%20of%20the%2021-year-old%20BTech%20final%20year%20student%2C%20Anil%20Kumar%2C%20on%20September%201.%20The%20student%20who%20refused%20to%20speak%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20student%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20both%20come%20from%20Schedule%20Caste%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20suicide%2C%20the%20IIT%20Delhi%20administration%20called%20an%20open%20house%20meeting%20on%20September%203%2C%20to%20address%20the%20suicide%2C%20and%20to%20understand%20what%20led%20to%20it%20and%20see%20whether%20the%20students%20wanted%20to%20flag%20issues%20they%20were%20facing%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20have%20raised%20a%20number%20of%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20life%20on%20campus%20%E2%80%93%20and%20said%20institutional%20harassment%20and%20discrimination%20based%20on%20caste%20is%20a%20daily%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20around%20this%20are%20only%20likely%20to%20get%20worse%20with%20another%20recent%20development%3A%20the%20Board%20of%20Student%20Publications%20circulated%20a%20campus-wide%20survey%20on%20caste%20discrimination%2C%20but%20this%20survey%20had%20to%20be%20withdrawn%20just%20hours%20later%20after%20students%20alleged%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%2C%20insensitive%2C%20and%20problematic%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcaste-discrimination-survey-in-iit-delhi-commenced-and-withdrawn%2Farticle67281936.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20institute%E2%80%99s%20SC%2FST%20Cell%20said%20it%20had%20not%20been%20consulted%20during%20the%20drafting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20student%20BTech%20final%20year%20student%20who%20died%20by%20suicide%20at%20IIT%20Delhi%20on%20September%201%20was%20not%20the%20only%20Dalit%20student%20to%20have%20ended%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20case%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20stated%20that%20the%20student%20was%20on%20degree%20extension%20as%20he%20failed%20to%20clear%20some%20exams.%20DCP%20(Southwest)%20Manoj%20C.%20had%20said%20that%20around%206%20pm%2C%20they%20received%20a%20PCR%20call%20regarding%20a%20suicide%20by%20a%20student%20at%20Vidyanchal%20Hostel.%20%E2%80%9COn%20verification%20of%20facts%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20a%20boy%2C%20Anil%20Kumar%2C%20enrolled%20in%20BTech%20in%20Mathematics%20and%20Computing%20(session%202019-2023)%20committed%20suicide%20by%20hanging%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20DCP.%20Police%20added%20that%20as%20he%20had%20not%20cleared%20a%20few%20subjects%2C%20he%20was%20residing%20in%20the%20hostel%20on%20a%20six-month%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Kumar%2C%20Ayush%20Ashna%20who%20was%20also%20from%20the%20mathematics%20department%2C%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%20on%20July%2010.%20Both%20students%20belonged%20to%20Scheduled%20Caste%20communities%2C%20and%20their%20treatment%20at%20the%20institution%2C%20many%20students%20said%2C%20may%20have%20pushed%20them%20over%20the%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20PhD%20student%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%20%E2%80%93%20a%20campus%20which%20also%20witnessed%20Dalit%20students%E2%80%99%20suicides%20%E2%80%93%20wishing%20anonymity%2C%20explained%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20SC%2FST%20students%20have%20faced%20harassment%20on%20these%20campuses%20where%20mostly%20faculty%20belong%20to%20the%20upper%20castes.%20The%20PhD%20student%2C%20who%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Ambedkar%20Phule%20Periyar%20Student%20Circle%20(APPSC)%2C%20said%20that%20reservation%20policies%20were%20not%20being%20followed%20during%20recruitment%20at%20IIT%20Bombay.%20APPSC%20students%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasteoncampus.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3Efiled%20RTIs%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20which%20it%20can%20be%20gleaned%20that%20around%2090%25%20faculty%20are%20upper%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20affects%20the%20overall%20atmosphere%20on%20campus%20and%20in%20classrooms.%20There%20is%20deep%20anti-reservation%20thought%20on%20campus.%20Teachers%20and%20students%20label%20reservations%20as%20anti-merit.%20Such%20an%20atmosphere%20and%20mindset%20on%20campus%20makes%20life%20difficult%20for%20SC%2FST%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20OBC%20student%20said.%20The%20student%20also%20said%20that%20casteism%20was%20manifesting%20itself%20on%20campus%20not%20just%20via%20professors%2C%20but%20several%20students%20also%20indulged%20in%20the%20same.%20%E2%80%9COne%20upper%20caste%20student%20had%20an%20SC%20roommate%3B%20they%20strictly%20asked%20the%20SC%20roommate%20to%20not%20touch%20and%20%E2%80%98pollute%E2%80%99%20their%20belongings.%20The%20SC%20roommate%20had%20to%20take%20a%20semester%20off%20to%20deal%20with%20this%20kind%20of%20casteist%20bullying%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20response%20to%20an%20RTI%20application%20filed%20by%20the%20APPSC%20of%20IIT%20Bombay%20on%20July%2029%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20in%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%2014%20departments%20had%20no%20faculty%20members%20belonging%20SC%20or%20ST%20communities%2C%2024%20departments%20lacked%20SC%20faculty%2C%2015%20departments%20lacked%20ST%20faculty%20and%20nine%20departments%20had%20no%20faculty%20from%20OBC%20groups.%20IIT%20Delhi%20has%20a%20total%20of%2027%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIITs%20are%20central%20universities%20and%20receive%20100%25%20funding%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20University%20Grants%20Commission%2C%20and%20are%20required%20to%20implement%20the%20reservation%20policy%20that%20apportions%2015%25%20seats%20to%20SCs%2C%207.5%25%20to%20STs%20and%2027%25%20to%20OBCs%20in%20faculty%20appointments%20and%20course%20admissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20January%202023%2C%20at%20least%20seven%20students%20from%20IITs%20across%20India%20have%20died%20by%20suicide.%20IIT%20Madras%20witnessed%20four%20deaths%2C%20while%20IIT%20Delhi%20saw%20two%20suicides%20and%20IIT%20Hyderabad%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstitutionalised%20pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20IIT%20Delhi%20students%20had%20released%20a%20statement%20which%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20the%20students%20of%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20condemn%20the%20institutionally%20engineered%20exclusion%2C%20apathy%2C%20and%20indifference%20that%20have%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20Dalit%20students%2C%20Ayush%20Ashna%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%2C%20in%20less%20than%20two%20months.%20This%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20crisis%2C%20and%20normal%20functioning%20must%20be%20temporarily%20suspended%20with%20immediate%20effect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDheeraj%20Singh%2C%20an%20alumnus%20of%20IIT%20and%20IIM%20who%20works%20on%20diversity%20in%20higher%20education%2C%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20situation%20at%20the%20IITs.%20To%20look%20deeper%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20speak%20for%20the%20students%2C%20Singh%20wrote%20to%20IIT%20Delhi%20director%20Professor%20Rangan%20Banerjee.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20sought%20an%20appointment%20with%20Director%20Prof%20Banerjee%20to%20speak%20about%20the%20matter%20of%20suicides%20on%20IIT%20Delhi%20campus.%20But%20we%20have%20to%20stop%20looking%20at%20this%20like%20an%20IIT%20problem.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20systemic%20problem%20of%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20which%20are%20in%20crying%20need%20for%20major%20reforms%20to%20make%20them%20safe%20and%20healthy%20spaces%20for%20weaker%20sections%20of%20society.%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20must%20look%20into%20how%20they%20can%20help%20such%20students%20thrive%20and%20implement%20laws%20for%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20eight%20suicides%20in%20eight%20months%20pointed%20to%20a%20systemic%20issue%20across%20IITs.%20%E2%80%9CI%20spoke%20to%20students%20from%20the%20same%20batch%20as%20Ayush%20and%20Anil.%20They%20have%20specifically%20told%20me%20that%20rank%20is%20an%20indirect%20caste%20marker%20to%20identify%20SC%2FST%20students%2C%20professors%20use%20casteist%20slurs%20privately%2C%20derive%20sadistic%20pleasure%20by%20failing%20students%2C%20professors%20refuse%20to%20give%20projects%20and%20recommendations%2C%20and%20placement%20companies%20use%20rank%20and%20CGPA%20as%20filters%20to%20weed%20out%20SC%2FST%20students.%20Around%2025%25%20of%20the%20Maths%20and%20Computing%20department%2C%20to%20which%20Ayush%20and%20Anil%20belonged%2C%20have%20their%20degrees%20on%20extension%20due%20to%20pride%20in%20failing%20students.%20These%20unhealthy%20practises%20need%20to%20stop%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwapnil%20Prasad%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%20from%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20attended%20the%20open%20house%20session%20called%20by%20the%20IIT%20administration%20with%20the%20students%20on%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20suicide.%20Prasad%20said%20that%20students%20shared%20the%20issues%20they%20face%20with%20the%20faculty%20during%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComments%20normalising%20cutthroat%20competitiveness%20are%20passed%20by%20professors.%20Academic%20rigour%20is%20expected%20out%20of%20us.%20Even%20very%20recently%2C%20a%20female%20student%20from%20BTech%20tried%20committing%20suicide%2C%20she%20was%20saved%20in%20time.%20We%20are%20also%20told%20that%20we%20must%20excel%20beyond%20expectation%20since%20we%20are%20at%20IITs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasad%20also%20shared%20the%20pressure%20and%20the%20whole%20atmosphere%20to%20being%20prepared%20to%20exhaust%20oneself%20at%20the%20institution%20has%20left%20many%20students%20with%20poor%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CCertain%20professors%20are%20unnecessarily%20failing%20students%2C%20they%20take%20pride%20in%20failing%20their%20students.%20How%20would%20this%20kind%20of%20intentional%20failing%20sit%20with%20students%20who%20reach%20IITs%20after%20years%20of%20hard%20work%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20issue%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fprofessor_drape%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%3EItisha%20Nagar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%20of%20Psychology%20at%20Delhi%20University%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20student%20suicides%20cannot%20be%20seen%20from%20an%20individualistic%20lens%2C%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20seen%20from%20a%20systemic%20lens.%20For%20certain%20economically%20weaker%20and%20marginalised%20families%2C%20Nagar%20explained%20that%20clearing%20exams%20at%20these%20institutions%20meant%20class%20mobility%20and%20having%20a%20better%20future.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20such%20pressure%20and%20anxiety%20associated%20with%20these%20institutions%20as%20students%20know%20that%20lakhs%20of%20students%20are%20appearing%20for%20few%20seats.%20In%20this%20atmosphere%2C%20with%20no%20mental%20health%20support%20and%20a%20reduced%20binary%20of%20self-evaluation%2C%20which%20is%20success%20and%20failure%20%E2%80%93%20then%20at%20that%20stage%20any%20kind%20of%20failure%20or%20even%20perceived%20failure%20can%20trigger%20students%20into%20taking%20their%20own%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagar%20views%20these%20suicides%20as%20systemic%2C%20pointing%20towards%20pressure%20from%20parents%2C%20unemployment%2C%20number%20of%20quality%20institutions%20and%20fewer%20seats%20in%20colleges%20as%20factors%20that%20increase%20anxiety%20among%20students.%20%E2%80%9CJust%20giving%20counselling%20to%20a%20student%20will%20not%20matter%20much%2C%20because%20society%20defines%20a%20%E2%80%98successful%E2%80%99%20student%20as%20someone%20who%20clears%20IITs%20or%20such%20competitive%20exams%20by%20defeating%20lakhs%20of%20other%20students.%20We%20need%20a%20society%20where%20a%20kid%E2%80%99s%20worth%20is%20tied%20to%20talent%20or%20extra-curricular%20activities%20or%20hobbies%20they%20enjoy%2C%20not%20marks%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694153422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13134317%2FIIT_Delhi_Entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftwo-dalit-students-suicides-in-two-months-highlight-institutionalised-discrimination-at-iits%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Students%20and%20alumni%20say%20that%20faculty%20members%20as%20well%20as%20other%20students%20routinely%20harass%20students%20from%20lower%20castes%2C%20and%20express%20anti-reservation%20sentiments%20openly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftwo-dal